aboutpara: Having enjoyed a rewarding 5-year career as a structural engineer in the construction industry, I have recently made a deliberate shift towards software development. To equip myself for this transition, I completed a rigorous 13-week software development bootcamp with Northcoder, where I honed my skills in various technologies.

resume.description: I am a software developer with a background in structural engineering. I have a passion for building web applications and automation tools. I am proficient in React, Node.js, and Python. I am currently seeking a full-time role as a software developer.
